# Todone API Documentation

## Overview
This document provides comprehensive API documentation for all services in the Todone application.

## Services

### Authentication Service
- `login(email: string, password: string)`: Authenticates user
- `register(userData: UserData)`: Registers new user
- `logout()`: Logs out current user

### Task Service
- `getTasks()`: Retrieves all tasks
- `createTask(taskData: TaskData)`: Creates new task
- `updateTask(taskId: string, updates: Partial<TaskData>)`: Updates existing task
- `deleteTask(taskId: string)`: Deletes task

### Project Service
- `getProjects()`: Retrieves all projects
- `createProject(projectData: ProjectData)`: Creates new project
- `updateProject(projectId: string, updates: Partial<ProjectData>)`: Updates existing project
- `deleteProject(projectId: string)`: Deletes project

## Usage Examples

```typescript
// Authentication example
const authService = new AuthService();
await authService.login('user@example.com', 'password123');

// Task example
const taskService = new TaskService();
const tasks = await taskService.getTasks();